Developer Terms of Use
des:
MyNorfolk allows people to report issues and get answers to your top questions about the City of Norfolk. Users can report the following issues and request the following services at https:// mynorfolk.org/ and MyNorfolk mobile apps.
 

- Submit Bulky Item Pick Up
 
- Report Collection Complaint

- Report Debris at Curb

- Report Trash and Debris
 
- Report Streetlight Outage

 
Get started by saying,

- "Alexa ask My Norfolk status of 272707"

- "Alexa ask My Norfolk what is the status of 272707"

- "Alexa ask My Norfolk to get the status of 272707" 

 
Note - You can use only the last numeric section of the Service Request Number to get the status. For example, just say 272707 instead of DaC2019-272707
